{"type": "article", "id": 25596, "title": "智能花园", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-18T07:08:40Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 33, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702140250jY2PQvWhrpIdKm9G.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">芬兰的团队 Plantui 开发了一种“智能花园”，绿色植物夹在一个被打开的圆球中间，就像一个胶囊。植物的生长不需要土壤或肥料，通过圆球上面内置的 LED 灯提供光合作用，底部的水泵则调节灌溉频率，非常方便。可以种植白菜、辣椒等蔬菜，从种子到成熟需要 5 到 8 周时间。Plantui 目前推出了三款产品，其中 Plantui6 获得了去年的红点奖。售价 99 欧元起，<a href=\"http://plantui.com/smart-gardens/plantui-6/\">这里是购买链接。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702140246RLjHCPFN8J0qZe9x.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.43\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702140247lTpXudtBUxzqmh2w.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75059952\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702140247RSpLt0hWNUO8XqIo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75136612\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702140248D2shbYBt0q6EZQGP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.45205479\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702140248k6tNlfV5hj3RiKEn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}